      "title": "React Error-Boundary Errors (componentStack)",
      "description": "Boundary errors only: context_source=react_boundary. Echo-SAFE by construction — Faro's console.error echo carries NO context_source, so no dedup filter is needed here (unlike the count panels). Surfaces context_componentStack. spec.md A4.",
