        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**p75, official CWV bands** (data is in **ms**; CLS unitless):\n\n| Vital | Good | Poor |\n|---|---|---|\n| LCP | <2.5s | ≥4s |\n| INP | <200ms | ≥500ms |\n| CLS | <0.1 | ≥0.25 |\n| FCP | <1.8s | ≥3s |\n| TTFB | <800ms | ≥1.8s |\n\nGreen = good, yellow = needs-improvement, red = poor. Fields are the full-precision `value_*` (not the rounded bare names)."
